{"tid":1458632,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人發現今日機場係效益最大嘅一次？ 無人被捕，影響大，國際都知","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T18:05:17.000Z","uid":259645,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1b4154955335b8fc3285cb9af7ebf44d3092b9","tid":1458632,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:33:30.000Z","msg":"諗下班狗有機會打9你仲洗唔洗放風呃你走?<br />\n<br />\n放得風即係佢冇能力打9你<br />\n<br />\n如果大家聽日去做多次，又搞到起唔到機，我會鄧政府好慘（不鼓吹）<br />\n<br />\n利申純以事論事，相信香港人人都係良好公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正：聽日再去<br />\n負：不了，怕怕"},{"pid":"619c4d0ca29acd557cd8acd057e4a3a4cffe0201","tid":1458632,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"聽日再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b38abaf94b95c48fe7a31a5c18d802042d78c3a","tid":1458632,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:43.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得太多post太亂？我整左個策略、行動、文宣方向精華集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7AT6Db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7AT6Db.png&h=b6163964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場檢討POST懶人包</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1</a><br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1</a><br />\n有消息嘗試用舉牌方式同人講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1</a><br />\n我覺得今日散水無錯，互屌先係真中計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1</a><br />\n[賽後檢討] 今日機場有無散水既都麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1</a><br />\n下次搞再機場唔該幫下啲旅客<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1</a><br />\n今日機場事件有少少諗法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1</a><br />\n我係散水撚，我係嚟道歉嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好需要你幫手報料/update/宣傳呀"},{"pid":"f8e737394ca5041050414bac0c10f259ba0856e1","tid":1458632,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c691af291637297fbe95d53c69efc8512ec27b8b","tid":1458632,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5172ec0c81731d925fc7b22ee8fc6e204f7910f2","tid":1458632,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fcc6dad9648e72a1d22785bdded4da684092dd59","tid":1458632,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5172ec0c81731d925fc7b22ee8fc6e204f7910f2","tid":1458632,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:39:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22dbc25373ef384c60f5d090674cb0c74ea3988b","tid":1458632,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84cf2b279dc9672db8a9526c550c87da3f030de4","tid":1458632,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"h